# Order of the Scales
Order of the Scales	KEY:Cavalier Order ~ Order of the Scales		CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:CavalierOrder.SpecialQuality																																																DESC:Members of this cavalier order serve the cause of legal integrity. Many order of the scales cavaliers track and apprehend fleeing lawbreakers so that these vagrants may answer for their crimes and make good on their debts.																																																						ABILITY:Special Ability|AUTOMATIC|Order of the Scales ~ Edicts|PREVARGTEQ:OrderAbilityLvl,1	ABILITY:Special Ability|AUTOMATIC|Order of the Scales ~ Challenge|PREVARGTEQ:OrderAbilityLvl,1	ABILITY:Special Ability|AUTOMATIC|Order of the Scales ~ Skills|PREVARGTEQ:OrderAbilityLvl,1	ABILITY:Special Ability|AUTOMATIC|Order of the Scales ~ Order Abilities|PREVARGTEQ:OrderAbilityLvl,1	ABILITY:Special Ability|AUTOMATIC|Order of the Scales ~ Mobile Wall|PREVARGTEQ:OrderAbilityLVL,2|PREVAREQ:OrderAbility2,0	ABILITY:Special Ability|AUTOMATIC|Order of the Scales ~ Seek Retribution|PREVARGTEQ:OrderAbilityLVL,8|PREVAREQ:OrderAbility8,0	ABILITY:Special Ability|AUTOMATIC|Order of the Scales ~ Sworn Oathkeeper|PREVARGTEQ:OrderAbilityLVL,15|PREVAREQ:OrderAbility15,0								SOURCEPAGE:p.22
Edicts			KEY:Order of the Scales ~ Edicts			CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:CavalierOrderAbility.SpecialQuality																																															DESC:The cavalier must fulfill all binding agreements he makes with others. If a bargain becomes impossible to fulfill, he must satisfactorily compensate all aggrieved or adversely affected parties involved in the bargain. When serving as a judge or arbiter, the cavalier must make fair, impartial judgments, and if unable to do so, must recuse himself at the earliest possibility. If authorized to enforce an agreement, the cavalier must wholeheartedly strive to accomplish this, remaining unswayed by threats, bribery, and other deterrents.																																																																																																																													SOURCEPAGE:p.22
Challenge			KEY:Order of the Scales ~ Challenge			CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:CavalierOrderAbility.SpecialQuality																																															DESC:Whenever an order of the scales cavalier issues a challenge, he receives a +1 morale bonus on combat maneuvers and attacks of opportunity made against the target ofhis challenge. This bonus increases by 1 for every 4 levels the cavalier possesses.																																																																																																																																																																													SOURCEPAGE:p.22
Skills			KEY:Order of the Scales ~ Skills			CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:CavalierOrderAbility.SpecialQuality																																															DESC:An order of the scales cavalier adds Knowledge (local) and Linguistics to his list of class skills. He gains a +%1 bonus on Sense Motive checks to determine whether someone bluffing and to determine whether a creature's behavior is being influenced by an enchantment.|max(floor(CavalierLVL/2)																																																																																																																																																															CSKILL:Knowledge (local)|Linguistics	SOURCEPAGE:p.22
Order Abilities		KEY:Order of the Scales ~ Order Abilities		CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:CavalierOrderAbility.SpecialQuality																																															DESC:A cavalier belonging to the order of the scales gains the following abilities as he increases in level.																																																																																																																																																																																																					SOURCEPAGE:p.22
Mobile Wall			KEY:Order of the Scales ~ Mobile Wall		CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Extraordinary.CavalierOrderAbility.SpecialQuality																																												DESC:The cavalier receives Step Up as a bonus feat. He can use this feat while mounted by succeeding at a DC 15 Ride check, directing his mount to move rather than himself. The cavalier gains a +%1 bonus to his CMD against attempts to tumble through squares he threatens.|floor(CavalierLVL+2/4)																																										ABILITY:FEAT|AUTOMATIC|Step Up																																																																																																																							SOURCEPAGE:p.22
Seek Retribution		KEY:Order of the Scales ~ Seek Retribution	CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Extraordinary.CavalierOrderAbility.SpecialQuality																																												DESC:Once per day after receiving a request for aid from a legal authority or an aggrieved party regarding the breaking of an oath, whenever the cavalier encounters the oath-breaking creature, he can choose to exact retribution. As a swift action, the cavalier can grant himself a +%1 bonus on all attack rolls, weapon damage rolls, and opposed checks against the oathbreaking creature. These bonuses last for %2 rounds.|CHA|CavalierLVL																																																																																																																																															SOURCEPAGE:p.22
Sworn Oathkeeper		KEY:Order of the Scales ~ Sworn Oathkeeper	CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Extraordinary.CavalierOrderAbility.SpecialQuality																																												DESC:the cavalier can formally witness an oath or agreement between two creatures. If either creature breaks or reneges on the agreement and the cavalier becomes aware of this, he gains the bonuses from his seek retribution ability against that creature at all times. This ability ends when the creature fulfills the conditions of the oath or receives just punishment for breaking the oath. The maximum number of witnessed oaths cavalier can have active at a time is %1.|CHA																																																																																																																																								SOURCEPAGE:p.22

